<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief uns <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
                        geschikt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und <expan>trewe<ex>n,</ex></expan> als
                        ir uns beweiset und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das umb ewch zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schuld<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wir
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        mit fleiss, wie sich die lewft und sache nu fürbas machen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, daz ir uns des ein
                                <expan>aigensch<ex>aft</ex></expan> und, sovil ewch füklich sey, bey
                        disem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet; das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
